@startuml RegisterMember
' ================================================
' Robustness Diagram: Register Member
' Library Management System | Prof. Walt Melo
' Group: G25
' ================================================

skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam monochrome true

title Robustness Diagram: Register Member\nGroup G25 - Library Management System

actor Librarian

' Boundary Objects
boundary "Registration\nScreen" as RegScreen <<Boundary>>
boundary "Member\nForm" as MemberForm <<Boundary>>

' Control Objects
control "Registration\nController" as RegController <<Control>>
control "ID\nGenerator" as IDGen <<Control>>

' Entity Objects
entity "Member\nDatabase" as MemberDB <<Entity>>
entity "Member" as Member <<Entity>>

' Flow
Librarian --> RegScreen : 1. Access
Librarian --> MemberForm : 2. Enter info

RegScreen --> RegController : 3. Process
MemberForm --> IDGen : 4. Validate

RegController --> MemberDB : 5. Check DB
IDGen --> Member : 6. Create

note right of RegController
  **Flow:**
  1. Access registration screen
  2. Enter member information
  3. Process registration request
  4. Validate and generate ID
  5. Check for duplicates
  6. Create member record
end note

@enduml
